      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;working-papers&#34;&gt;Working papers&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paper&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-title-row&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;jmp-badge&#34;&gt;Job market paper&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;paper-title&#34;&gt;Information, Coordination and Welfare in Equity Financing&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;!-- &lt;div class=&#34;paper-abstract&#34;&gt;[Add your abstract here.]&lt;/div&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paper&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-title&#34;&gt;Bank Competition, Productivity and Inequality&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;!-- &lt;div class=&#34;paper-abstract&#34;&gt;[Add your abstract here.]&lt;/div&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paper&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-title&#34;&gt;Household Assets and the Job Ladder&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-coauthors&#34;&gt;with Madeline Hanson&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;!-- &lt;div class=&#34;paper-abstract&#34;&gt;[Add your abstract here.]&lt;/div&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;publications&#34;&gt;Publications&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paper&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-031-22653-3_9&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Trade in Value-Added: Does MFN Status Matter for Colombian Regions?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-coauthors&#34;&gt;with R.P. Fernandes, I.F. Araújo, and E.A. Haddad&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;paper-abstract&#34;&gt;&#xA;    In &lt;em&gt;The Colombian Economy and Its Regional Structural Challenges&lt;/em&gt;, Springer, 2023.&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
